            "text": "<p>Combining Vitamin C, Vitamin E, Ferulic Acid and patented EDAFENCE® technology, the ENDOCARE RADIANCE range helps defend against oxidative stress while visibly improving skin brightness and luminosity. Ideal for customers seeking brighter, more even-looking skin.</p>",
